name: SABDO PALON NAGIH JANJI
description:
Sabdo Palon is a mythological triumph of the Javanese people in ancient times.
Sabdo Palon declared his oath to return to Java 500 years after the collapse of Majapahit.
it is said that the arrival of Sabdo Palon will be accompanied by various disasters, he comes with anger because the land of Java is full of error and chaos.

1200x1200 px
